  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151180/extras/7ce80a8376f88903e67e0b1a6cd7167c.avif?t=1592509052\" width=560 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About the game</strong></h2>Hardcore platformer about a big-eyed toad named Cucho. One morning a hungry cat woke up a toad. Cucho, having discovered that the cat food is over, goes to the supermarket. On the way, he met a magical power that moved him to an unknown world. The player has to help Cucho return home and feed his arrogant pet.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 4 planets and 1 space platform<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151180/extras/d3c9f3d571def476aec987c7c50b76ec.avif?t=1592509052\" width=560 height=100 /></span><br><br></li><li> Learn new abilities<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151180/extras/518b4d469d79c2b96fc944dc97e9a07a.avif?t=1592509052\" width=560 height=100 /></span><br><br></li><li>  Epic Boss fights<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151180/extras/5aac8ea18e8bb39a1b86697e58b2c37d.avif?t=1592509052\" width=560 height=100 /></span><br><br></li><li> Nice drum and bass soundtrack<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151180/extras/fa0ccbfa15282a2a0ebf0118278a8978.avif?t=1592509052\" width=560 height=100 /></span><br><br></li><li> Sloth!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151180/extras/79cb87e09cd0cfb837b91e34970e2165.avif?t=1592509052\" width=560 height=100 /></span></li></ul>",
